    Black Aracnia looked the bot up and down. He was strong, and most likely 
could be controlled if she played her cards right.
    "I want to take you to the Predacons, but, its currently under the 
control of a bureratic dictator. I want to put myself on the throne. Help me 
and I can promise you endless victory for the Predacons!"
    She smiled, "What do you say?" And then put her claw on Thunder Hammers 
shoulder.

    Paralysis watched Darkmouse, smileing.
